: 0, "author": 114079}, {"id": 6164, "content": "说说你为什么要这儿来，能跟我们分享你的故事吗…分享你妹啊！！这是唱歌比赛，唠家常出门左转不送！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134619}, {"id": 6165, "content": "自以为自己很牛逼其实在胡萝卜的停不下来的导师，自以为很牛逼做作的停不下来的演技实力派选手，明明是演技大赛嘛。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149986}, {"id": 6144, "content": "那些被声泪俱下说出的所谓音乐理想不过是幻像，评委观众节目组，都是这些幻想的消费者。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149916}, {"id": 6149, "content": "听的听的就哭了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124680}, {"id": 6150, "content": "飙高音就有转身", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136608}, {"id": 6151, "content": "唱歌比赛是可以有的，但你麻痹的，你能不能不再说你那些逗逼身世，傻x梦想，二炮证明自己等等，我们就想听个歌，唱完能不能滚犊子，让下面接着赶紧唱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149967}, {"id": 6414, "content": "选手好多回锅肉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151089}, {"id": 6670, "content": "不飚高音难道就不能晋级了嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152105}, {"id": 7699, "content": "还没唱先说身世，没说身世先哭一顿，边哭评委边安慰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158342}, {"id": 6688, "content": "好吧，很久不看唱歌选秀节目了。看吐槽都Get不到点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152198}, {"id": 6950, "content": "明明清泉音，刻意烟枪嗓。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146167}, {"id": 6185, "content": "测试", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 6186, "content": "测试", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 6187, "content": "感觉看比赛就像在刷QQ空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103843}, {"id": 6188, "content": "娱乐下而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 6451, "content": "总是翻唱，你连自己的作品都没有，你参赛干什么！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124369}, {"id": 7476, "content": "广告比唱歌时间都长", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 94841}, {"id": 6208, "content": "唱歌——歌唱，两个字，说着不同的意思，唱歌是理性的，歌唱是感性的，大家觉得呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150180}, {"id": 6213, "content": "直接讓選手們唱廣告主題曲就不必費心植入廣告了(¯▽¯)~", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150197}, {"id": 6216, "content": "我要唱歌，但首先我得告诉你我有多惨", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140770}, {"id": 6736, "content": "你的梦想是什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123244}, {"id": 6744, "content": "其实每次都是想看他们撕逼而已，歌基本都听多了，感觉差不多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152365}, {"id": 6237, "content": "反正我都不认识", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146756}, {"id": 6497, "content": "我不想听故事...", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151574}, {"id": 6763, "content": "广告好长", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148367}, {"id": 6253, "content": "听的太多身世传奇，我都怀疑我自己活着是干啥。。。好吧，最后连同情心都弄没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147499}, {"id": 4462, "content": "声泪俱下讲身世", "image": null, "praise_count": 676, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4463, "content": "报名次能报两个世纪", "image": null, "praise_count": 227, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 6767, "content": "其实……，但是……。我只想……。我的选择是……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149115}, {"id": 4465, "content": "现场观众太浮夸", "image": null, "praise_count": 359, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4467, "content": "评委不专业还啰嗦，每次我都只看选手唱歌的视频片段", "image": null, "praise_count": 257, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4468, "content": "花样作死，也是不懂转椅子蒙脸跟唱歌有什么关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 6772, "content": "点评不真诚 假得我头发都卷了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152542}, {"id": 4469, "content": "我喜欢的歌手老是被一些唱的不怎么样的淘汰了", "image": null, "praise_count": 174, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4470, "content": "最好不要准时开始看因为前面会有一大段开场白", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 6777, "content": "比惨了啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151439}, {"id": 6272, "content": "不喜欢主要是广告的节目上插播比赛片段", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139724}]}